This event will feature outstanding artists from different music sectors of Nepal, including popular singers such as Shanti Shree Pariyar Bujel, Joti Batha Magar, Karishma Dhakal, and Rachana Rimal.

CEO of Fly Nepa Travel and Tours, Binod Adhikari, mentioned, "This event is primarily focused on the Nepali festival Teej, which will be celebrated from July to September. Through this event, Abba Nachha America aims to help the Nepali community feel at home."

